        'Day Trips ‚Ü≥ ‚â§320 ¬∑ Shows ‚Ü≥ ‚â§160 ¬∑ Local Tastes ‚â§240 ¬∑ Michelin <p> ‚â§80 ¬∑ '
        'Downtown <p> ‚â§80 ¬∑ Restaurants Near Hotel <p> ‚â§80 ¬∑ '
        'Getting Around ride-app rows ‚â§80 ¬∑ Getting Around tram block ‚â§400 '
